The paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques, specifically long short-term memory (LSTM) networks, to improve streamflow forecasting. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the integration of different types of data, which falls under the category of data integration (cs.SI) and computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE).
